			<p>Calculate the perimeter of a semi-circle (half circle) with radius 60 miles.</p>
		</statement>
	</task>
	<task>
		<statement>
			<p>Calculate the perimeter of a quarter of a circle with radius 60 miles.</p>
		</statement>
	</task>
	<task>
